The design has been created within a plum color scheme and features the number 20, center top, with each of the numbers, 2 and 0 in a decorative text box. The numbers are written in an elegantly curved font with a digitally created gold foil effect overlay and set against a black background. In the lower section of the design, on a gently curved, multi-bordered text box, is the text ‘Happy Anniversary’, written in a beautifully flowing, script style font, with decorative swashes. This text too has a digitally created, gold foil effect overlay and is set against a black background.
